captions.text:
Live from Daytona Beach, Florida, it's the
2013 NHSCA Cheer Nationals! There's gonna

be flips, there's gonna be spirit, there's
gonna be a whole lot of words being spelled

out with people's arms! So sit back, relax,
and prepare to enjoy the finest competitors

in America's most prestigious fake sport only
on TWAT: Television for Women and Tweens.

Let's go down to our hosts, modeling agent
Jeannie Halverstad and the former voice of
the National Football League, Bert Hickey.

Well I, along with the rest of our capacity
crowd, am extremely excited about this year's
competition. What about you, Bert?

Five months ago, I was announcing the Super
Bowl. Now I'm commenting on a glorified PE
class.

Well, maybe you wouldn't have lost your job
if you hadn't been so liberal with your use
of the n-word on national television.

The power was out in the stadium! I thought
the mics were down!

Nonetheless, I think we can expect these girls
to show us the nation's finest cheerleading

all while maintaining poise, confidence, and
the utmost in elegance. We'll be right back
after this. You're watching TWAT.
And cut!

Jesus titty fucking Christ, can somebody get
Bert a cup of coffee! And a mint! Goddamn,

what did you have for breakfast, a bottle
of Dewar's?
I also had a bagel!
Well you smell like a skunk's taint.
I'm a legend!

Oh please, you're one scandal away from being
the new head coach at Penn State.
Oh, too soon.

Fuck off, now where the hell is my nonfat
skinny caramel hazelnut jamocha cappucino?

Imagine my surprise when it turns out it did
not say, "Welcome to Flo Rida!"

Okay ladies, lock it up. We've reached the
promised land. Cheer Nationals!
Jesus Christ, what a fucking shitshow!
Cut!
Ugh, what now?

I think you meant to say fudging poop-show.
Now that's a ruined take! Do you know how
much that costs us?

Well, actually, we're shooting digital, so
it doesn't even-

Shut up Brett! Shut your little tiny girl
mouth. If your mother wasn't my mistress,

I never would have hired you. Now do you want
to be famous?
Yes.

Well then how bout you keep your trashy little
fuck me mouth clean from now on?
Fine.

Wait, um, I'm confused. Are we- is this a
TV show.
Our entire lives are TV shows.

What? Wait, and why is the French girl on
the team now?

Oh, do you not remember? I was le victor of
the cheer tryouts!
We had cheer tryouts? What the-

Yes, and by the way, Saison, I'm really glad
that this is the week you decided to start
showing.

Yes, the baby inside of me is bursting forth
like a legionnaire inside of my how do you
say...
Stomach! Inside of your stomach! God!

Actually I was going to my say my how do you
say, uterus.
Son of a-
Son of a gun! Son of a freaking gun! Arrrrrggghhhh!!!!

Oh what do we have here? The Overland Park
Cheer Squad, huh? I've heard a lot about you

girls. You think you're hot shit, huh? Well,
the Staten Island School for Girls is gonna

put you in your fucking place. In fact, why
don't we make a little wager, bitches.

Well, actually we already have a squad that's
our arch-rivals, so-
We do?

Yeah, we've got a whole wager and a whole
backstory thing going so-

Oh my God, so sorry. Here I am like an asshole,
hey do you know if Austin has a rival yet?
No, I don't think so...

Hey Austin, you bunch of hipster cowboy weirdos,
who the fuck are you?
Who the fuck are you, partner?
Trisha, where is Ashley Katchadourian?

Well, she texted me saying she'd be here promptly
at 9:45. And in case you're wondering, I did

make sure it was am. I'm not an idiot. But
we didn't discuss time zones.

Well if it isn't the Overland Park Cheer Squad
and their head cheerleader, Vin Diesel.

Oh, that's funny Tanya. Why don't you go-
You're such a- Ugh! Brittnay, I can't curse.
Will you handle this?
Gladly! Listen here you bunch of little-
We're rolling!
Ugh! Right. Jenna, I can't curse. Handle it.
Okay, but who exactly are these girls?
Oh, they seem very nice!

Oh my god, for the love of- Trisha! It's up
to you!

Trisha, you're the only one that can curse.
I need you to put these b-words in their place.
Right! Okay! I'm sorry about this.
Do what you must!

I'll never forget you. You girls are shit
from a butt that smells like bitch. Which

is what you are as well so fuck in your butts
all the shit that bitches are. And, and, you

fuck that shit that's all in your butt, and
you put it in the f- the bitch that is your
face, cause you're a f-

Oh my god, Trisha, Trisha, please- Trisha
please stop.
Oh my god. How did I do?
You were great!
You're alive!
Yeah?

Aww, that's cute, but you'll have to excuse
us if we're not too intimidated by some poop
in our butt jokes.

That was like being cursed out like a Mad
Lib. Is that really all you girls have?
Ugh,brr, egh, ummm...
Ugh,brr, egh, ummm...
Your attention please!

Oh if you'll excuse me, my future agent is
speaking. I should probably listen.

Ladies can we gather around, please. When
I get off this stage, you'd better have an

iced coffee with three bars of Xanax ground
into it. Today's competition is about to begin.

And remember ladies, today's festivities are
not just about cheerleading. I'll also have

my eye out for potential clients at the Halverstad
modeling agency. Who knows, today one of you

could go from part-time model to semi-full
time model or if you're lucky, seasonal full
time model.

Hey boo-boo, heard you broke up with your
boyfriend. Don't worry bout it, I'm gonna
own that ass all day today.
Ha, ha right back at you Taylor.

And I don't care if you're thin, short, tall
or fat. After all, Wal-Mart casts commercials

too. No what I'm looking for is a big smile,
maybe a cute little button nose, and most

definitely a full head of luscious lovely
hair.

Well, two out of three ain't bad. I'm kidding.
It's terrible.

Oh my god, I don't think it's ever gonna come
back! You look like Sinead O'Connor. What's
wrong with you?

Well, I tell you what, it's not the heat that
gets you. It's the humidity.
You're telling me! Wearing a tie was a mistake!
Hey guys! What are you doing here?

Oh well, my girlfriend and Blaine's girlfriend
are both cheering in this competition.
Plus, I wanted to be here to support my son.

Yes Blaine, I'm sure that you'll be nominated
for the almost father of the year award.
What are you doing here Tanner?

Oh well, Tristan and I actually do this every
year.

Well hello boys, having fun? How could you
not?! Honey, I just found out that in 15 minutes,

there's going to be a flexibility workshop
in the convention center annex. They're gonna

teach us how to do the splitz. I don't think
I need to tell you that I'm gonna be going,

but I mean I guess I just did! How adorbs
am I right now?

That sounds fun, sweetie. But I think I'll
just hang out with the guys.

Oh, sounds good, we were just gonna go get
some hot dogs.

Oh hot dogs! I love food shaped like penises!
You know, because I'm gay!

Goddamit, Jonathan! How the fuck did you get
here?
Uh, gee, let me think. An airplane, idiot.
Right, but why are you here in Daytona Beach?

I followed them here! You wouldn't understand
though. It's a gay thing.
No, it's not. It's a stalker thing.

Oh how sweet, it's like a little gay Homeward
Bound. Than, you should be Chance, Tanner

you're definitely Shadow, and I get to be
Sally Field! Rowr!

Alright, so a couple of dick dogs, and then
you guys wanna troll for some strange?
Ughhhh...
It doesn't get more strange.

So because of those eighteen reasons, pyrotechnics
will not be allowed this year. Have a good

competition girls! I'll be keeping my eyes
open! Happy cheering!
Great speech, Jeannie!

Oh, thanks for the newsflash, it's what I
do for a living, dipshit.
It's okay, it's okay, Angie, it's okay.

Well, Mackenzie, you may want to leave now
and spare your scalp the stress of losing.
You know what, Tanya-
Oh hey guys, hope I didn't miss anything important.
Ugh, there you are!

It's Florida, why the hell are you wearing
a trenchcoat.

Oh yes, I suppose things are heating up in
here, aren't they?

Oh Mackenzie, have you met the newest member
of the Atchison High Cheer Squad? Ashley Katchadorian?
WHAT THE-

Ah, ah, ah Mackenzie, wouldn't want to lose
more hair right now, would you?
You little-
Ah, ixnay on the ursing-cay, umbass-day!

Ok, if I wasn't confused before, I sure as
fuck am now.

Well, I'll leave you girls to mull over these
recent developments. Ladies, let's go gather

up the rest of our squad. We have a national
championship to win!
Haha! Bitch!
Well, I guess that's it.
We are so...screwed.

What did we ever do to Ashley Katchadorian?
Oh wait, oh my God.
What are we gonna do now?

There's nothing we can do. We're not gonna
be allowed to cheer with five members. We

might as well pack our bags, go home, and
kiss Oak Park Mall goodbye one last time.
Not so fast!

Oh, great, the robot girl. Whatever the fuck
that means. Jesus Christ.

Alright, so, okay, um, thank- thank you for
all the lessons, I just wanted to, like, let's
just freestyle, like-
Oh my god, I would love to freestyle.

Off the top of my head, okay, alright, here
we go.
Go.
Alright, alright. Bitch.
Oh. Cock. Oh god!
Uh, uh, uh, uh, uh, fuck!
I was gonna say fuck!
Don't worry, there's like so many!
Uh, shit!
Okay, alright, alright... gallbladder!
Is that a curse word?

Well, I mean, it sounds like one, it sounds
real dirty.

OMG you're right, it sounds super dirty! Motherfucking
cunt gallbladder!
Yeah!
Yeah, take that in your gallbladder, you bitch!

Shove it. Shove a penis in your gallbladder,
yeah!
